COMMENT ON FUNCTION "battles"."fn_auto_finalize_battles"() IS 'Called by pg_cron every 5 minutes. Phase 1: voting→scoring for expired battles. Phase 2: scoring→closed via fn_battles_finalize. Returns count finalized. Errors per-battle are caught and logged to audit.events.';



